name: Proslis
content:
Proslis was a Garwian male envoy of the Garwian Unity nation in the Unknown Regions. Around 19 BBY, Chiss Senior Captain Mitth'raw'nuruodo "Thrawn" and Caregiver Mitth'ali'astov "Thalias required passage to the Vak Combine nation, undected and under false identities. They were able to arrage passage with Garwian Second Defense Overlord Frangelic, who gave them a place on Proslis' diplomatic ship.
Proslis was mentioned in the 2020 novel Thrawn Ascendancy: Chaos Rising, the first installment of Timothy Zahn's Star Wars: The Ascendancy Trilogy.
